title: Tandoori Salmon Bowl with Barley
method: Heat oven to 200°C (tray-bake) or prep base for bowls.
Toss protein and veg with sauce and oil; roast 18–25 min.
Serve over base, add herbs/lemon to finish.
swaps: Swap base for brown rice to keep it approachable.
Use tofu/beans to make it vegetarian.
hydrationTip: Add a glass of water; tray-bakes can be salty if using sauces.
